title: Friendly talk
body:
So I kinda raged at riot and posted a DFG prob discussion but lets put that aside.


How's your day people?

replies.body: Well OT, i managed to get my 3rd Ocean Week Point before the Last Achievement dropped so im happy. Ive noticed a lot of people arnt playing very well after the reset (myself included), or that im getting matched up with higher elos more often. It seems that even normals MMR is being effected.

yeah, we don't want Veigar to  one shot.

So bye {{item:3128}}
